text: Fabrizio Ronechetti (born 26 June 1985 in Uruguay) is a Uruguayan footballer who now plays for A.D. Carmelita in Costa Rica.Carmelita se reforzó con el atacante Fabrizio Ronchetti Yashin Quesada ==Career== Ronchetti started his senior career with Juventud de Las Piedras.
